AnkiLernu — Your daily Esperanto learning companion
===================================================

AnkiLernu is a proof of concept.

It's a web interface for generating Esperanto flashcards for
Anki. Vocabulary is retrieved from Lernu’s dictionary and cached to
avoid flooding.

AnkiLernu is free software distributed under GNU Affero General Public
License v3.0 or later.

Dependencies
------------

- PHP >= 8.2
- cURL extension for PHP
- MySQL extension for PHP
- MySQL/MariaDB
